(author: jayem)
(date: 2026)
(Store captured BEAM XY + probe RPM.)
(Uses #5501-#5503 — NOT G30/toolsetter #5181-#5183.)
(#1 = BEAM X G53 mm, #2 = BEAM Y G53 mm, #3 = probe RPM)
(Prefer direct MDI #5501=... from the UI; this sub is a fallback.)

o<laser_set_start_xy> sub
    #<bx> = #1
    #<by> = #2
    #<rpm> = #3
    #5501 = #<bx>
    #5502 = #<by>
    #5503 = #<rpm>
    (DEBUG, LASER: BEAM XY #5501/#5502, probe RPM #5503)
o<laser_set_start_xy> endsub

M2
